The following changes were made to the original C code (from 2022-10-27):

- Added Python module as `asapmodule.c`: adds a modified version of asap.c/main()
- The option for only outputting spart files was ignored

- Workarounds for Unix-only includes and strcasestr()
- Different names for output files

- Add mafftio.c, import mafftio.h, wrapping standard output

- Source diff between original and modified code:

